Title: Fix host label search in monitoring search and quicksearch
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1660661527
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.2.0b1

If host labels were searched with "hl:" prefix in previous 2.1 versions, no
search results were found, even if the search matched.

